  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt; 18

          -  Breast cancer treated by neo-adjuvant chemotherapy (T&gt;2cm)

          -  Measurable lesions ,assessed clinically and by ultrasound

          -  Delay minimum between biopsy and PET: 15 days

          -  PS-WHO: 0

        Exclusion Criteria:

